name: Test create build configuration for project | UI
description: Create new user, project and build configuration | UI

steps.name: Generate project data
Create project manually with name: drive, id: sMB3CLes8wU
Click project selector from header to go to projects page
Click selector: "[data-test-title="Projects"]"
Click selector: "a[title="Create new project"]"
Create project manually
Click selector to create project manually
Click selector: "a[href="#createManually"]"
Fill manual project creation form with name = "drive", id = "sMB3CLes8wU", desc=""
Fill selector: "input#name" with text: "drive"
Fill selector: "input#externalId" with text: "sMB3CLes8wU"
Fill selector: "input#description" with text: ""
Click create project button with selector input#createProject
Click selector: "input#createProject"
Check if project with id: sMB3CLes8wU was created
Check if project with locator: sMB3CLes8wU exists on server with 5 retries
Sending GET request to http://localhost:8111/app/rest/projects/id:sMB3CLes8wU with data: None, expected_status: 200
Generate fake build conf data for project with id: sMB3CLes8wU
Create build configuration for project with id: sMB3CLes8wU
Go to build configuration creation page: http://localhost:8111/admin/createObjectMenu.html?projectId=sMB3CLes8wU&showMode=createBuildTypeMenu&cameFromUrl#createManually
Load url: http://localhost:8111/admin/createObjectMenu.html?projectId=sMB3CLes8wU&showMode=createBuildTypeMenu&cameFromUrl#createManually
Click selector to create project manually
Click selector: "a[href="#createManually"]"
Fill build conf creation form
Fill selector: "input#buildTypeName" with text: "live"
Fill selector: "input#buildTypeExternalId" with text: "EAnjHI38RnK"
Fill selector: "input#description" with text: ""
Click button: input[name="createBuildType"] to create manual build conf
Click selector: "input[name="createBuildType"]"
Wait for successful build conf creation by waiting selector: div.successMessage:has-text("successfully")
Wait for selector: "div.successMessage:has-text("successfully")"
Check if build configuration with fake build conf id: EAnjHI38RnK was created
Check if project with locator: sMB3CLes8wU exists on server with 5 retries
Sending GET request to http://localhost:8111/app/rest/projects/id:sMB3CLes8wU with data: None, expected_status: 200
